#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:10
#: af8cc001e6df4208812386c7819fa69d
msgid ""
"Core management scripts rewrite with better structure and extensibility, "
"`current API documentation <https://dev.qubes-os.org/projects/core-"
"admin/en/latest/>`__ and the documentation API index as a `webarchive "
"<https://web.archive.org/web/20230128102821/https://dev.qubes-"
"os.org/projects/qubes-core-admin/en/latest/>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:12
#: 019e93271504483a857e85582265dd27
msgid ""
"`Admin API <https://www.qubes-os.org/news/2017/06/27/qubes-admin-api/>`__ "
"allowing strictly controlled managing from non-dom0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:14
#: 7ee19a42f08047f999643425776ca809
msgid "All ``qvm-*`` command-line tools rewritten, some options have changed"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:16
#: df4a0d3c8484481db389eda83612634a
msgid ""
"Renaming VM directly is prohibited, there is GUI to clone under new name and"
" remove old VM"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:18
#: c53bbef306f74e738a0675767ce5a116
msgid ""
"Use `PVH <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"secpack/blob/master/QSBs/qsb-037-2018.txt>`__ and `HVM "
"<https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/2185>`__ by default to "
"`mitigate Meltdown & Spectre <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"secpack/blob/master/QSBs/qsb-037-2018.txt>`__ and lower the `attack surface "
"on Xen <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"secpack/blob/master/QSBs/qsb-024-2016.txt>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:20
#: 29fdb6ec781e4a6291fed87ff0035e37
msgid "Create USB VM by default"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:22
#: 3afc44af535743478614f546dbf62bbb
msgid ""
"`Multiple DisposableVMs templates support <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"issues/issues/2253>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:24
#: 475c3bfa46294aafb15d02a4d10e8609
msgid ""
"New :doc:`backup format </user/how-to-guides/backup-emergency-restore-v4>` "
"using scrypt key-derivation function"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:26
#: bb37f248b13949dcb53659504185e0a6
msgid "Non-encrypted backups no longer supported"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:28
#: eb5dd16ad412422e9c3a85368a0a750c
msgid ""
"`split VM packages <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/2771>`__,"
" for better support minimal, specialized templates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:30
#: db65bca6b7994314b2076edcf14d0a86
msgid ""
"`Qubes Manager decomposition <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"issues/issues/2132>`__ - domains and devices widgets instead of full Qubes "
"Manager; devices widget support also USB"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:32
#: 09d73ae68a45464ebe7a1a8a187f7e2b
msgid ""
":doc:`More flexible firewall interface </developer/debugging/vm-interface>` "
"for ease unikernel integration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:34
#: 805a8ee83eef4951bbe9c25230146469
msgid ""
"Template VMs do not have network interface by default, `qrexec-based updates"
" proxy <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/1854>`__ is used "
"instead"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:36
#: a5b4823261c74153a473373206845f77
msgid ""
"More flexible IP addressing for VMs - `custom IP "
"<https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/1477>`__, `hidden from the "
"IP <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/1143>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:38
#: f55411e6634b4132818d3e12f96c7bc4
msgid ""
"More flexible Qubes RPC policy - `related ticket "
"<https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/865>`__, :ref:`documentation"
" <developer/services/qrexec:specifying vms: tags, types, targets, etc.>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:40
#: fa19fa2d7b924ff7abd72f65be6ae7cf
msgid ""
"`New Qubes RPC confirmation window <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"issues/issues/910>`__, including option to specify destination VM"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:42
#: adfc50235140462f9cc1d803cb7bb42a
msgid ""
"`New storage subsystem design <https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-"
"issues/issues/1842>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/4_0/release-notes.rst:44
#: 44443853bbe2482ca81a65d41e11d06c
msgid "Dom0 update to Fedora 25 for better hardware support"
msgstr ""

